('freed-ai', 'Freed', 'AI scribe for clinicians that produces SOAP notes from patient encounters',
 E'Freed is an AI scribe focused specifically on clinician productivity and note quality. The platform records patient encounters (in person or via video), transcribes the conversation, and generates structured SOAP notes that match the clinician''s personal documentation style. The personalization layer is the differentiator - Freed learns each clinician''s preferred phrasing, note structure, and template patterns over time.\n\nThe workflow is designed to fit existing clinician routines without requiring EHR replacement. Notes are generated in 60 seconds after the encounter ends, then the clinician reviews, edits, and pastes into their EHR. The platform supports outpatient consultations, telehealth visits, and inpatient rounds. Freed targets primary care, internal medicine, pediatrics, and specialties where consultation-based documentation is the bottleneck.\n\nFreed is priced per-clinician at $99-$129/month with annual billing options. The platform is HIPAA-compliant with BAA available for covered entities. Reviews from clinicians consistently emphasize the time savings and the quality of personalized note style after 2-3 weeks of use.',
 'https://getfreed.ai', 'https://getfreed.ai',
