('ambience-healthcare', 'Ambience Healthcare', 'AI operating system for clinicians with documentation and decision support',
 E'Ambience Healthcare positions itself as an AI operating system for clinicians, going beyond documentation to include clinical decision support, coding assistance, and care plan generation. The platform handles ambient note documentation similar to Heidi and DeepScribe, but extends into adjacent clinician workflows: documentation, coding, prior authorization drafting, referral letter writing, and patient instructions generation.\n\nThe consolidation thesis is the differentiator. Rather than buying separate AI scribes, coding assistants, and prior auth tools, clinicians use Ambience as a unified AI layer across their daily work. The platform integrates with Epic, Cerner, and other major EHRs, with action-taking capabilities that reduce administrative burden beyond simple note generation. Health system deployments report meaningful provider satisfaction and burnout reduction metrics.\n\nAmbience targets large health systems and academic medical centers rather than solo practices or small groups. Pricing is custom and structured around clinician licenses plus implementation services. The company has raised significant funding from healthcare-focused investors and has deployment partnerships with major academic medical centers including Cleveland Clinic.',
