('tempus-ai', 'Tempus AI', 'Precision medicine platform with AI-powered diagnostics and clinical trial matching',
 E'Tempus AI is a precision medicine platform that combines genomic sequencing, clinical data, AI analytics, and trial matching to support oncologists, neurologists, and cardiologists making complex treatment decisions. The platform sequences patient tumors or other tissue samples, integrates results with clinical history, and applies AI models to surface treatment options including FDA-approved therapies, off-label uses, and clinical trial enrollment opportunities.\n\nFor oncology specifically, Tempus has built one of the largest real-world clinical-genomic datasets in the United States. This data powers AI models that predict treatment response, identify resistance mechanisms, and surface trial opportunities tailored to each patient''s molecular profile. Cancer centers using Tempus report meaningful improvement in molecular tumor board efficiency and trial enrollment rates.\n\nTempus partners with cancer centers, hospital systems, and pharmaceutical companies. The company went public in 2024 (NASDAQ: TEM) and has expanded beyond oncology into cardiology and neurology applications. Pricing is structured around sequencing tests (per-test) plus platform access licenses for clinical decision support tools. Reimbursement for the genomic sequencing component varies by payer and condition.',
 'https://tempus.com', 'https://tempus.com',
