 ARRAY['One of the largest real-world clinical-genomic datasets in the United States', 'AI-powered treatment recommendation and clinical trial matching', 'Multi-specialty platform: oncology, cardiology, neurology', 'Public company (NASDAQ: TEM) with mature clinical and pharma partnerships'],
 ARRAY['Custom enterprise pricing varies by test volume and platform access tier', 'Reimbursement for genomic sequencing varies by payer and condition', 'Best ROI requires significant patient volume in covered specialties', 'Implementation involves sample logistics and EHR integration complexity'],
